dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Depths shown by bathymetric tints and isolines. Wall map. Historic Maps copy has label affixed to verso of map: Geological map of Dutch East Indies. London : Edward Stanford Ltd., cartographers to His Majesty ... London agents for the sale of Ordnance maps.
